snippet.title: Amber heard rekindles romance with elon musk
snippet.description:
Amber heard rekindles romance with elon musk 
The Magic Mike XXL star and the Tesla CEO – who split up last August due to their busy schedules – have been spotted together several times in Los Angeles in the last month, sparking speculation that they have reconciled. A source has told the New York Post Page Six column “They are together at the moment.” Amber, 31, and Elon, 46, were seen holding hands at dinner on Monday, 22 January. They were also spotted sharing breakfast in LA, and kissing outside a restaurant. article continues below The...
